{
    "_description": "ThinkPHP 6.x / think-orm-specific DB symbol equivalence pack (option 4 of docs/plans/orm-db-semantic-dedup.md). Extends the stock DbOpRegistry with think-orm method names that aren't covered by the generic CRUD-verb pattern. Use with --profile=db-aware-thinkorm together with --db-aware to fold ThinkORM call shapes into the same canonical __DB_<OP>__ tokens as the rest of the recognised DB ecosystem. ThinkORM follows the ActiveRecord pattern with methods like find(), select(), insert(), update(), delete(), and aggregation helpers like count(), sum(), avg(), min(), max(). See https://github.com/topthink/think-orm",
    "db_symbols": {
